<h2>You got new releases</h2>

<p>Hello <%= @user.uid %>, looks like you have some new album releases. Awesome!</p>

<br />

<ul>
  <% @releases.each do |album| %>
    <li>
      <%= link_to album.name, "https://open.spotify.com/album/#{album.spotify_id}" %>
      by <%= album.artist.name %>
      was released on <%= I18n.l(album.released_at, format: :short_with_year) %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>I hope you enjoy!</p>

<p>Best,</p>

<p>Matias L.</p>
